Introduction

FUN LITTLE NEW CANYON OFF PALMER CANYON. WE WERE LOOKING FOR SOMETHING ELSE BUT FOUND THIS SHORT PLAY CANYON. NOT MUCH TO IT, BUT STILL A NICE ONE TO GO THROUGH. THIS WAS THE SECOND SMALL CANYON WE DID WHILE WE WERE IN PALMER CANYON.
